5:
Pork, peas, onion, carrot... Think I
tasted pineapple too...
9:
What're you mutterin' to yourself
about?
12:
Oh, it's just the synthesized food we
ate earlier... I'm trying to figure out
the flavors.
15:
It was all SoyMate, right? Why do
you care so much?
18:
I can't help wondering how they
made it...
21:
What seasonings did they use... And
how'd they manage that sour tang?
25:
You have a problem, pal. A coo-coo
for cooking problem.
34:
Clear me some space! This target's
mine!
48:
I sure do. You got a problem with
that, punk?
53:
Are... you modded up? Wow, you
totally look like a real tiger!
58:
Oh, you're from a different world,
huh? That's pretty awesome! No
wonder everything seemed off.
60:
Where do you find other worlds,
anyways?
63:
Eh, whatever. Sorry for the mix-up!
I'm on the hunt for a big white tiger,
so you can see why I got confused.
66: You're looking for a tiger in this town?
69:
Yeah, it escaped from a research
facility. They asked me to make sure
it got back unharmed.
73:
Unharmed? With the way you came
at me?
76:
Hey, I was only gonna knock you out.
Just a little jolt, that's all!
79:
Anyway, it's an open job, so whoever
nabs it first gets the rewardâ€”a nice
one too, from what I heard!
80:
If you see the tiger, give me a holler.
I'll come running!
85:
Uh, are we just supposed to shout,
or...
89:
You can call me if you need help
too. Consider it an apology for
earlier! See ya!
95:
There he goes... Must be running on
a schedule.
99:
Well, yeah. They've got lab freaks on
the loose. This world's a mess.
102:
You say that like other worlds don't
have their own monsters...
114:
He mixed me up with UGLY?! Guy
must be dumb, blind, or both.
120:
I don't want him to think we're trying
to take the prize money.
139:
I've got the best mods for my ears
and feet! Just say my name, and I'll
come running!
142: So is that the tiger then?
146:
Huh, looks a lot scarier than I
pictured.
149:
You gonna wet your pants, scaredy
cat? Need us to lend a paw?
154:
Oh, put a sock in it! I can do this on
my own! Watch me!
159:
Maximum power, no holds barred!
I'm not gonna lose to the likes of you!
164: Did the power just... go out?
171: Teurgis, what did you just do?
174:
Oh, you know, a little illegal mod
here, a little extra plasma in my
blade there, and the output levels
go a little crazy...
177: Anyway, we better get out of here!
183:
You're my accomplices now! If you
don't wanna pay for repairs, then
move it!
192:
Come on, take us to that world of
yours!
206:
Damn, this is good! You're a genius,
Alk! This tastes exactly like
synthesized food but a hundred
times better!
207:
Man... I had no idea natural
ingredients had this flavor...
210:
Will you finally go home after you
finish eating?
212:
You kidding? This place is awesome!
I'm gonna stay here for the time
being!
221:
Teurgis. Called himself a
troubleshooter or something and
invited himself along.
223:
He's more like a trouble maker if you
ask me though...
